Package: gpkg
Type: Package
Title: Utilities for OGC GeoPackages
Version: 0.0.1.9001
Author: Andrew G. Brown
Maintainer: Andrew Brown <brown.andrewg@gmail.com>
Description: High-level wrapper functions to build GeoPackages containing a variety of different data. Read/write of spatial vector and gridded data is performed using standard GDAL utilities. Additional functions are provided to manipulate attributes and tabular data.
Imports: 
    DBI
Suggests: 
    RSQLite,
    terra,
    tinytest
License: GPL-3 + file LICENSE
Depends: R (>= 3.1.0)
RoxygenNote: 7.1.2
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
